data.description: Welcome to 7519 Summer Shore! This beautiful home features: 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, Primary bedroom on first floor with double vanity, Jetted tub + sperate shower, and large walk-in closet. If you're looking for a home that is almost 4,000 square feet, this is the one! Luxury Vinyl Planks throughout the first floor + stairs. Gas log fireplace to compliment the living area with high ceilings. Beautiful porcelain tile Carrera white flooring throughout the kitchen and bathrooms, granite counter tops, kitchen island with white cabinets, formal dining + breakfast area. Upstairs area features, new floors, large game room, 3 bedrooms + secondary full bath. For nice Texas weather, you and your family can enjoy the beautiful backyard with a covered patio. Additional bonuses, Solar panels, Solar screen windows, keep the house nice and cool, and Water Filtration system. Easy access to Hwy 59, restaurants and shopping right outside the neighborhood. Come take a look!
